text:
django + memcached

django model:
* Server:
    STR name UNIQUE
    STR alias
    IP ip
    STR key

* UsageLog:
    Server server
    DATETIME datetime
    CpuUsage cpu
    MemoryUsage memory
    LIST(DiskUsage) disk
    LIST(ProcessUsage) process
    LIST(ErrorLog) error
    
* CpuUsage:
    DECIMAL user
    DECIMAL system
    DECIMAL idle

* MemoryUsage:
    INT swap_total
    INT swap_used
    INT virt_avail
    INT virt_total
    INT virt_used

* DiskUsage:
    STR device_name
    STR fs_type
    STR mount_point
    INT used
    INT total
  
* ProcessUsage:
    ENUM(cpu, mem) type 
    INT order
    DECIMAL cpu
    DECIMAL memory
    STR name
    
* ErrorLog:
    DATETIME datetime
    TEXT log
